<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Mount Pleasant</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A peaceful residential neighborhood located in the north-west quadrant of Calgary, Mount Pleasant lies immediately north of the community of <a href="/rosedale.php">Rosedale</a> and is bound by the Confederation Park on the west and north.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">A breathtaking neighborhood in NW Calgary, the community in Mount Pleasant houses some of the most highly sought after residential properties in the entire city. </p>
        </div>
